data.description: This beautifully maintained 3 bedroom, two bath home is gracefully situated on a quiet road within walking distance to the lake. Gracious entry welcomes you with a vaulted ceiling, a fireplace and hardwood floors. Spacious living room is begging for a large gathering with a conjoined bonus area that could be used for a cozy home office, playroom, etc with french door leading out to the large deck and private backyard. Bonus room could easily be used as a 1st floor guest quarters. Large primary bedroom with a Jack and Jill bath and two charming and bright bedrooms make up the 2nd floor.Tranquil, picturesque STR friendly community boasts two lakes, beach area, outdoor  pool and clubhouse. Minutes from Kalahari Water Park, Camelback Ski Resort, Pocono Premier Outlets and Rt 80.
